Colleen Harris, 73, was found guilty of first-degree murder on Wednesday after shooting her third husband Robert 'Bob' Harris in 2013 .
She will be sentenced on June 5, standing to receive 50 years to life for the murder .
In 1985, she shot dead her second husband and the father of her three children, 46-year-old James Batten, after claiming he had been abusive towards her .
Both killings were carried out in the same home with the same type of gun .